ntial oil has a high linalool content, and there’s research to suggest inhaling the aroma of linalool has a positive impact on the receptors in our brains that facilitate a more peaceful and rested state. In turn, this creates the right framework to encourage an easier passage to sleep.’\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW-320-80.jpg\" alt=\"A closeup of lavender growing in a stone planter\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/SuvegwDvsuN47bqmKmc7RW.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Getty Images)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eOf course, when it comes to \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/bedroom/how-to-choose-a-pillow\" data-url=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/bedroom/how-to-choose-a-pillow\" data-hl-processed=\"none\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"/bedroom/how-to-choose-a-pillow\"\u003ehow to choose a pillow\u003c/a\u003e, there\u0026#39;s more to it than simply opting for one with an infusion of sleep-inducing lavender. That\u0026#39;s because the \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/bedroom/best-pillow-for-side-sleepers\" data-url=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/bedroom/best-pillow-for-side-sleepers\" data-hl-processed=\"none\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"/bedroom/best-pillow-for-side-sleepers\"\u003ebest pillow for a side sleeper\u003c/a\u003e will be very different in shape and support to the kind of pillow a back or front sleeper needs.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe good news is that there are plenty of ways to benefit from the relaxing powers of lavender without opting for a dedicated aromatherapy pillow. Instead, you could find the right pillow for your support needs, and then introduce the calming effects of lavender into your bedroom in other ways.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026#39;A light mist of diluted lavender essential oil (2-3 sprays) can create a calming environment without being overpowering,\u0026#39; shares perfumer, scent designer, and founder of \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.humos.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-url=\"https://www.humos.co.uk/\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-hl-processed=\"none\"\u003eHUMOS\u003c/a\u003e, Gabriel De Carvalho.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-newsletterForm-articleInbodyContent-Kf3qejBj8DQZaQ2sUASffh\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026#39;Running a diffuser with lavender oil for around 30 minutes before bedtime can enhance relaxation,\u0026#39; or, \u0026#39;when diluted with a carrier oil, applying lavender oil to pulse points (such as the wrists or neck) may also promote a sense of calm before sleep.\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"section-alternatives\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAlternatives\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv data-id=\"88d64539-a8fa-4f1b-883a-6d79a775e397\"\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://www.awin1.com/awclick.php?awinmid=6091\u0026amp;awinaffid=103504\u0026amp;clickref=idealhome-gb-4651720822897621866\u0026amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Fuk%2Flisting%2F677533770%2Fsleepy-head-pillow-spray-with-lavender%3Fgpla%3D1%26gao%3D1%26%26gQT%3D2\" data-model-name=\"Made by Coopers Sleepy Head Pillow Spray\" data-url=\"https://www.etsy.com/uk/listing/677533770/sleepy-head-pillow-spray-with-lavender?gpla=1\u0026amp;gao=1\u0026amp;\u0026amp;gQT=2\" target=\"_blank\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" rel=\"sponsored noopener\" data-hl-processed=\"hawklinks\" data-placeholder-url=\"https://www.awin1.com/awclick.php?awinmid=6091\u0026amp;awinaffid=103504\u0026amp;clickref=hawk-custom-tracking\u0026amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etsy.com%2Fuk%2Flisting%2F677533770%2Fsleepy-head-pillow-spray-with-lavender%3Fgpla%3D1%26gao%3D1%26%26gQT%3D2\" data-google-interstitial=\"false\" data-merchant-name=\"Etsy UK \u0026amp; I\" data-merchant-id=\"8756\" data-merchant-network=\"AW\" data-merchant-url=\"etsy.com\"\u003e\u003cp data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/eW