me.co.uk%2Fbedroom%2Faldi-wellbeing-lavender-scented-pillow-launch\" data-google-interstitial=\"false\" data-merchant-name=\"SkimLinks - dreemdistillery.co.uk\" data-merchant-network=\"SkimLinks\"\u003e\u003cp data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd-320-80.jpg\" alt=\"Dreem Distillery Bed Balm\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/LHxv2XsZHEZ65n76aPFuNd.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDreem Distillery Bed Balm\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eMassage a small amount of the lavender-infused Dreem Distillery Bed Balm onto the temples and chest before bed to relieve tension and prepare for deep slumber.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eHowever, you choose to bring the scent of lavender into your bedroom, whether that\u0026#39;s via the Silentnight Wellbeing Lavender Scented Pillow or one of our other suggestions, it\u0026#39;s clear this natural sleep aid has a lot to teach us about \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/bedroom/bedroom-advice/how-to-sleep-better-192220\" data-url=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/bedroom/bedroom-advice/how-to-sleep-better-192220\" data-hl-processed=\"none\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"/bedroom/bedroom-advice/how-to-sleep-better-192220\"\u003ehow to sleep better\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘Several studies have shown that inhaling lavender essential oil before bed is linked to longer sleep duration, improved sleep efficiency, and reduced symptoms of insomnia,’ confirms Gabriel De Carvalho, ‘particularly in those with mild sleep disturbances or anxiety-related sleep disorders.’\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eOne recent scientific study ‘indicated that lavender increases slow-wave sleep – the deep sleep stage essential for physical recovery and memory consolidation,’ another found that inhaling lavender leads to \u0026#39;calming and sedative effects’.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP-320-80.jpg\" alt=\"A cream bedroom with a stone column bedside table and a tufted, fringe-trimmed rug\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/MrTf4PWhdw4XA3gPYjfskP.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Future PLC/Anna Stathaki)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘Lavender has also been found to lower cortisol levels (the body\u0026#39;s primary stress hormone), which can contribute to better sleep,’ continues Carvalho.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAnd yet further research demonstrates that ‘lavender inhalation has been associated with a reduction in heart rate, blood pressure, and respiratory rate, which all contribute to a relaxed state conducive to sleep. Lavender oil inhalation lowered sympathetic nervous system activity – the system responsible for the “fight-or-flight” response – helping the body transition into a restful state.’\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePersonally, I\u0026#39;m convinced. How about you? Are you going to try incorporating lavender into your bedtime routine?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
